OL,3,CUnite boss admits fresh talks with
OL,4,Ccouncil over Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,FThe union boss leading Birmingham's
OL,7,Fstriking bin workers has admitted
OL,8,Fholding fresh "talks" with the council
OL,9,Fafter the authority walked out of
OL,10,Fnegotiations last summer.
OL,12,FSharon Graham, general secretary of
OL,13,FUnite the Union, made the comments to
OL,14,FITV News Central while joining workers
OL,15,Fon a picket line on Thursday morning.
OL,17,FShe said discussions had taken place
OL,18,Fwith "a number of people", including
OL,19,F"some people at the council", but
OL,20,Fwould not confirm whether the talks
OL,21,Fwere formal.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@UO]zD@FOUzD@YO]{D@AOU{D@\O]
