FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774012288
OL,3,CUnite boss admits fresh talks with
OL,4,Ccouncil over Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,F"As you would imagine, talks have been
OL,7,Fgoing on," she said.
OL,9,F"My conversations have been with a
OL,10,Fnumber of people inside the council
OL,11,Fand outside.
OL,13,FShe continued: "These are talks about
OL,14,Fthe fact that we need to get the deal
OL,15,Fback on the table."
OL,17,FThe long-running dispute has seen
OL,18,Frefuse workers take industrial action
OL,19,Fin a row over changes to job roles and
OL,20,Freductions in pay.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@JO]qD@AOUuD@POUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774012288
OL,3,CUnite boss admits fresh talks with
OL,4,Ccouncil over Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,FGraham said a previous 'ballpark deal'
OL,7,Fhad been discussed with the council
OL,8,Fbut was never formally put forward.
OL,10,F"We scoped out a deal that the council
OL,11,Fsaid they thought was a good deal,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,F"We said that we could put that deal
OL,15,Fto our members. The council left the
OL,16,Froom and then said the commissioners
OL,17,Fblocked the deal."
OL,19,FShe insisted the agreement should
OL,20,Fstill be honoured.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@cO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774012288
OL,3,CUnite boss admits fresh talks with
OL,4,Ccouncil over Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,FGraham added there was now "a real
OL,7,Fclear understanding" among those she
OL,8,Fhad spoken to that the deal should be
OL,9,Freconsidered.
OL,11,F"There's a clear understanding from a
OL,12,Fnumber of people," she said, declining
OL,13,Fto give further details of discussions
OL,14,Fwith government or other groups.
OL,16,F"I'm not going to talk and rehearse
OL,17,Fwhat I'm speaking to government about
OL,18,For what I'm speaking to other groups
OL,19,Fabout because it would be wrong."
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@TO]sD@AOUtD@RO]xD@AOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
