OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774012288
OL,3,CUnite boss admits fresh talks with
OL,4,Ccouncil over Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,FShe reiterated that any agreement
OL,7,Fwould ultimately be decided by union
OL,8,Fmembers.
OL,10,F"Deals go to members ` members vote on
OL,11,Fdeals," she said.
OL,13,FLast week, the council's cabinet
OL,14,Fmember for environment, Majid Mahmood,
OL,15,Frefused to say when the authority last
OL,16,Fspoke with Unite.
OL,18,FHe said: "I don't directly deal with
OL,19,Fnegotiations, that's a question for
OL,20,Fcouncil officers."
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@GO]zD@JOU|D@RO]
